import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
// main.js
import ElementUI from 'element-ui'
import 'element-ui/packages/theme-chalk/lib/index.css' // 引入样式文件
Vue.use(ElementUI)
Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  router,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
